Off-The-Record-Messaging plugin for Psi

This is a Off-The-Record-Messaging plugin for the Psi instant messenger.
https://psi-im.org/

See the file INSTALL for instructions how to build this plugin.

Please note that the plugin may be instable and security is not guaranteed.

See http://www.cypherpunks.ca/otr/ for more information about OTR.


